    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this vehicle in truly exceptional condition. Maintained to the most exacting standards, this unit displays no discernible wear and retains its original showroom luster. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to uncompromising care. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a vehicle that mirrors its factory-delivered state in every respect. Performance and aesthetics are in perfect alignment, offering an experience indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 46500.0,
